cohortName: Respiratory syncytial virus infection referent incident cohort
logicDescription: Persons with condition occurrence of referent concept (437222) or descendants, for the first time in the person's history. Persons exit cohort at the end of the observation period.

cohortName: Respiratory syncytial virus infection referent prevalent cohort
logicDescription: Persons with condition occurrence of referent concept (437222) or descendants, for the first time in the person's history, with at least 365 days of prior continuous observation. Persons exit cohort at the end of the observation period.

cohortName: Respiratory syncytial virus infection prevalent cohort during a hospitalization
Respiratory syncytial virus infection hospitalization with an RSV test w/in 7 days
Respiratory syncytial virus infection with an RSV test w/in 7 days
Respiratory syncytial virus infection and (Hospitalized OR RSV Test w/in 7 Days OR 2nd DX w/in 7 days)
